# tkv2 - raw HTML escape hatch public API

Slice `tkv2-raw-html`: `rawHtml` builds a trusted raw-markup `TkNode` while
`rawText` remains escaped text. DOM serialization is covered by the emitted
SPA/jsdom gate for this slice; this conformance file keeps the public API and
lowering path live on both lanes.

[rawText, rawHtml, fragment_](std/ui/reactive.ssc)
[lower](std/ui/lower.ssc)
[defaultTheme](std/ui/theme.ssc)

```scalascript
val escaped = rawText("<strong>escaped</strong>")
val raw = rawHtml("<strong data-x=\"ok\">raw</strong>")
val view = lower(fragment_(escaped, raw), defaultTheme)

println("raw-html-built")
```
